---
title: Veggie and Ricotta Flatbreads with Basil-Arugula Salad
description: Marinara sauce and luscious ricotta with a kick of heat are a match made in flatbread heaven! After exiting the oven with perfectly crisp crusts and melt-in-your-mouth ricotta, these flatbreads are topped off with a refreshing balsamic-dressed arugula and basil salad. Talk about a treat for the taste buds!
